ActMigratory Birds Convention Act, 1994
SubjectRegulations Amending the Migratory Bird Sanctuary Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the MIGRATORY BIRD SANCTUARY REGULATIONS in order to (1) rename seven Migratory Bird Sanctuaries (MBS) in the Nunavut Settlement Area with Inukitut names identified by the Area Co-Management Committee (ACMC) responsible for each of the MBS; and (2) create a new part XIII to the Schedule for MBS formerly located in the Northwest Territories and now located in Nunavut.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2025-0099 Publication Date: 2025-03-26
AttachmentsAttachment
